OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims raise concerns
OL,4,Cover drop in Jersey conviction rates
OL,6,FFewer than 10% of recorded incidents
OL,7,Fof domestic abuse in Jersey
OL,8,Fsuccessfully resulted in a conviction
OL,9,Fin 2024, new data has revealed.
OL,11,FA Freedom of Information request by
OL,12,FITV News has revealed that in 2024,
OL,13,Fthere were 482 recorded incidents of
OL,14,Fdomestic abuse crimes and 254 arrests
OL,15,Fwere made.
OL,17,FOnly 42 of these cases resulted in a
OL,18,Fsuccessful conviction.
