OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims raise concerns
OL,4,Cover drop in Jersey conviction rates
OL,6,FFurther, the figures show that the
OL,7,Frate of conviction for these types of
OL,8,Fcrimes has dropped over the past five
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FThe rate of successful convictions in
OL,12,Fthe UK has also remained low: 2.78% in
OL,13,F2024.
OL,15,FAccording to The Office for National
OL,16,FStatistics, the police recorded 1.4
OL,17,Fmillion incidents of domestic abuse in
OL,18,Fthis year - of these, 39,000 resulted
OL,19,Fin criminal convictions.
