OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims raise concerns
OL,4,Cover drop in Jersey conviction rates
OL,6,FHowever, survivors of domestic abuse
OL,7,Fsay the figures in Jersey are still
OL,8,Fdisappointing.
OL,10,FSuzannah Mahe was attacked and raped
OL,11,Fby former Jersey restaurant owner
OL,12,FGavin Neil Roberts. He was jailed for
OL,13,F15 years.
OL,15,F"The outcome I received was amazing,
OL,16,Fand I'm so grateful the system worked
OL,17,Fin my favour," Suzannah explained.
OL,19,F"I was believed, but for many, that
OL,20,Fisn't the case."
