OL,3,CDomestic abuse victims raise concerns
OL,4,Cover drop in Jersey conviction rates
OL,6,FWhen responding to the figures, she
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's disappointing, but I
OL,8,Funderstand why it doesn't happen as
OL,9,Foften as many victims are scared to
OL,10,Fcome forward."
OL,12,FThe island's Head of Crime, Detective
OL,13,FSuperintendent Alison Fossey, says
OL,14,Fthat Jersey Police are working to
OL,15,Fsecure more convictions for domestic
OL,16,Fabuse, but that the difficulty lies in
OL,17,Fthe complexity of these crimes.
